data.title: All My Children
data.meta_description: All My Children (1970) starring Bobbie Eakes, Michael E. Knight, Susan Lucci and directed by Conal O'Brien.
data.text: All My Children is an American television soap opera that aired on ABC for 41 years, from January 5, 1970 to September 23, 2011, and on The Online Network since April 29, 2013 via Hulu, Hulu Plus, and iTunes. Created by Agnes Nixon, All My Children is set in Pine Valley, Pennsylvania, a fictitious suburb of Philadelphia which is modeled on the actual Philadelphia suburb of Rosemont.
